text: allahale nai timimadhyebata timro nimti joriharuko srsti garyo ra svasnibata timra choraharu ra natiharuko srsti garyo ra khanako nimti timila'i ramra ramra khanekura diyo, ta ke yiniharule taipani jhutha kuraharuma visvasa rakhdachan ra allahabata di'eka upaharaharuprati krtadhnata prakata garnechan
